              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin target samples of natural thallium, 29.5% Tl-203",
                "and 70.5% Tl-205, were prepared by electrodepositing",
                "thallium onto 10-mum thick Cu-foils, 10-mm diameter.",
                "The deposit thicknesses of thallium layers on the",
                "different foils were between 10-15-mum according to the",
                "deposition current value.",
                " 50-mum thick Al-foil were used as catcher foils.",
                "The sandwich Al-Tl-Cu was used. The natural copper",
                "foils, 99.99% were used backing material serve also as",
                "energy degrader of proton beam and as beam monitors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " High-pure germanium detector absolute efficiency",
                "of about 42% relative to Na(I) detector  was used to",
                "measure the activity of each sandwich Al-Tl-Cu and Cu-",
                "monitor foil in the stack for about 60-min after the",
                "end of the bombardment. The detector efficiencies for",
                "various counting distances and photon energies were",
                "determined using Ba-133, Co-60, Cs-137, Th-229 and",
                "Ra-226 standard sources."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "CYCLO"
                ],
                "institute": "3SARSAR"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The TCC Cs-30 cyclotron in King Faisal",
                " Specialist Hospital and Research Center."
              ]
            }
          ],
