            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The experimental cross section for Tl-nat(p,xn)",
                " reactions were compared with the cross-sections",
                " recommended by the IAEA and with earlier published",
                " data when it was possible.",
                " The integral yields of the produced radionuclides were",
                " calculated from the measured excitation functions."
              ]
